<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222067>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Astyanax pirabitira, UFRGS 4861, 81.0 mm SL, paratype. Upper and lower jaw teeth, right side, medial view. Scale bars = 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/222067/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222066>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Astyanax pirabitira, MCP 47707, 53.9 mm SL, holotype, rio das Antas, border between Cambará do Sul and Bom Jesus, Rio Grande do Sul, Brazil. Scale bar = 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/222066/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222068>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Map of southern Brazil and Uruguay, showing the distribution of the examined material of Astyanax pirabitira. A = rio das Antas, laguna dos Patos system, and P = rio Pelotas, rio Uruguay basin. Some symbols represent more than one lot or locality. Red circle = type locality." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/222068/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

